# Root Memory

- For every substantial user request, update `rules/memory/USER_PROMPTS_LOG.md`.
- Record major session decisions, files read, and outcomes in `RESEARCH_JOURNAL.md`.
- If multi-agent coordination matters, update `rules/memory/AGENT_INTERACTIONS_LOG.md`.
- Keep root memory about global coordination, not local project internals.
- Prefer traceability over brevity when context may matter for future research writing.
